{
  "stem": "142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- they knew it-- you do it once, twice, a few times, and you know that is a routine going on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because always it was from 1,500 to 2,500 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they-- they knew exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They never brought things except when really they-- they think it was necessary.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that is when-- and they accommodate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The undressing room?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CHUCKLING] You had to pick up-- we had to pick up everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything goes to Germany or wherever it was, or.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only thing they left was, I think, the-- the food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think they used to put it in trucks or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't-- they were pretty organized.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't do it, but they did it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we hear a couple of times, you know, that there were somebody in there they didn't know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a-- it was a very young child or something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think once or twice I heard some, because sometime, you know, after the-- there were-- the-- the gas came in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a couple of times we went in, we see maybe a very-- not me, but [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Morris ?] once saw a very small guy that was alive after, you know, because probably the-- the mother wanted to catch up and-- and maybe he can save it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The German came in, gave him a shot, and boom, I'm finished, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were very-- the Germans were very good at executing people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was in the-- the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The undressing area, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the Germans would come in and kill him-- finished.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was 30 minutes, because they-- they were waiting for us to come in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the ventilation should start.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
